Videos of the panel presentations and Q&A sessions should be available soon on
the [Castan Centre YouTube](https://www.youtube.com/user/CastanCentre/videos)
channel. There is also a series of videos [Have You Got That
Right?](http://www.haveyougotthatright.com/#video) that explores a wide range
of topics.

The author attended the event as a media representative on behalf of Global
Voices. Members of the GV community have been guest speakers at previous
conferences, namely [Sami Ben
Gharbia](https://castancentre.com/2012/07/31/short-and-long-videos-from-
our-2012-conference-tunisian-blogger-sami-ben-gharbia/) and [Jillian
York](https://youtu.be/GnEI3OI1c3Y). The author's Twitter Moment of the
conference can be viewed
[here](https://twitter.com/i/moments/1021947908025802753).

